	This original Margo neem soap is made from pure neem oil which is crushed from the hand-picked leaves and seeds of the neem tree, contains 35 biologically active principals and has anti-bacterial, anti-inflammatory and anti-fungal properties. Neem is a widely used resource in South East Asia, particularly in India and has proven antibacterial properties that provide deep cleansing and protect the skin. This neem soap contains vitamin E and other essential amino acids making it an excellent natural moisturising base for the skin to help maintain its natural moisture balance, for healthy and clean skin.</p>
